Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd teach you something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,about the world of Mahjong ringers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,AKAGI SHIGERU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:10.29,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,If this goes on we'll lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to go "all or nothing" more than anyone.\NThat's Akagi's true nature
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the ONLY chink through which I can stab at him
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll aim there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:27.01,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,4th Game\NSouth Hand 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaaay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. 4 dora?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A Haneman win
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:53.97,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,Haneman: 18,000/12,000 points dealer/non-dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:01:00.68,Default - white - top,,0,0,0,,Game 4\NSouth Hand 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi's luck has been running near 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in good shape for a Tsumo win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The wall is overflowing with Akagi's winning draws
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten, what do you mean to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite of 100% luck is 0% luck
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncanny luck will be mine
